OL,6,FA former prosecutor who was trapped by
OL,7,Fpolice plotting to rape a seven-year-
OL,8,Fold girl has been jailed.
OL,10,FClive Jones, 74, was arrested after
OL,11,Fcommunicating with an undercover
OL,12,Fofficer posing as a woman who was
OL,13,Foffering to arrange a meeting with her
OL,14,Fdaughter.
OL,16,FThe former lawyer, who prosecuted
OL,17,Fcases at Hull and Bridlington
OL,18,Fmagistrates' courts for many years and
OL,19,Fbecame a district crown prosecutor,
OL,20,Fhad condoms, ropes and Viagra in his
OL,21,Fcar when he set off to meet the girl.
