OL,3,CEx-prosecutor caught plotting to rape
OL,4,Cseven-year-old girl
OL,6,FHe was convicted by a jury at Durham
OL,7,FCrown Court after a six-day trial in
OL,8,FDecember.JThe case had been moved from
OL,9,FHull Crown Court because of his links
OL,10,Fto the local justice system.
OL,11,FSentencing him, Judge James Adkin told
OL,12,FJones: "The evidence against you in
OL,13,Fthe trial was abundant and
OL,14,Fcompelling."JThe offences that Jones
OL,15,Fintended to commit were "utterly
OL,16,Frepellent", the judge added.
OL,17,FThroughout the hearing, Jones could be
OL,18,Fheard repeatedly coughing and sighing.
OL,19,FHe occasionally put his head in his
OL,20,Fhands.JHelen Chapman, mitigating, said
OL,21,Fhis wife had continued to stand by
OL,22,FJones.
