OL,3,CEx-prosecutor caught plotting to rape
OL,4,Cseven-year-old girl
OL,6,F"He is fortunate to receive the
OL,7,Fsupport of his wife, who is present
OL,8,Ftoday and has been a pillar of support
OL,9,Fto him," she said
OL,11,FThe effect of a prison sentence would
OL,12,F"reverberate" on to her. "She is
OL,13,Fsomebody who will feel his loss very
OL,14,Fkeenly," said Miss Chapman.JJones was
OL,15,Fjailed for 12 years and given a 20-
OL,16,Fyear sexual harm prevention order. He
OL,17,Fmust register as a sex offender for
OL,18,Flife.
